MALACAÑANG Manila

PROCLAMATION NO. 459

RESERVING FOR OFFICE SITE PURPOSES OF THE DEPARTMENT OF ENVIRONMENT AND NATURAL RESOURCES (DENR) PROVINCIAL AND COMMUNITY ENVIRONMENT AND NATURAL RESOURCES OFFICES, A CERTAIN PARCEL OF LAND OF THE PUBLIC DOMAIN, SITUATED AT BARANGAY TELAJE, MUNICIPALITY OF TANDAG, PROVINCE OF SURIGAO DEL SUR, ISLAND OF MINDANAO

Upon recommendation of the Secretary of Environment and Natural Resources and by virtue of the powers vested in me by law, I, GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO, President of the Republic of the Philippines, do hereby withdraw from sale, or settlement and reserve for office site purposes for the use of the Provincial and Community Environment and Natural Resources in Surigao del Sur Offices under the administration of the Department of Environment and Natural Resources, subject to private rights, if there be any, a certain parcel of land of the public domain situated in Barangay Telaje, Municipality of Tandag, Province of Surigao del Sur, Island of Mindanao, which parcel of land is more particularly described as follows:

LOT NO. 4371-D, CSD-116819-011071-D

A PARCEL OF LAND (Lot 4371-D, Csd-116819-011071-D), identical to Lot 4416, Cad-392-D, Tandag, Cadastre, situated in the Barangay of Telaje, Municipality of Tandag, Province of Surigao del Sur, Island of Mindanao. Bounded on the NE., along line 1-2 by Lot 4371-C, Csd-116819-011071-D; lines 2-4 by Lot 3965, Cad 392-D, Tandag Cadastre; on the SE., and NW., along lines 4-7-1 by lot 4371-E, Csd-116819-011071-D, identical to Lot 4417, Cad 392-D, Tandag Cadastre. Beginning at the point marked “1” on the plan being S., 28 deg. 01 ‘W., 1055.90 meters from BLLM No. 1 of Cad 392-D, Tandag Cadastre, thence;

46.90 m to point 2;

11.05 m to point 3;

28.00 m to point 4;

69.51 m to point 5

99.06 m to point 6;

54.46 m to point 7;

48.96 m to point 8;

46.90 m to point 2;

beginning, containing an area of SIX THOUSAND NINE HUNDRED NINETY ONE (6,991) SQUARE METERS. All point referred to are indicated on the plan and marked on the ground as follows: Point 3 by old pt. Cyl. conc. mons. 15×60 cms. and the rest by PS cyl. conc. mons. bearing grid; Date of Subdivision survey, January 13-14, 1992, executed by Geodetic Engineer Trazon B. Guda and approved on April 8, 1992.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF , I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

DONE in the City of Manila, this 9TH day of September, in the year of Our Lord, Two Thousand and Three.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: (Sgd.) ALBERTO G. ROMULO Executive Secretary

Source: CDAsia

Proclamation No. 459, September 9, 2003
